17 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
18 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 3310 of Title 63, unless there
19 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
20 In the event a public trust hospital enters into a joint venture
21 or acquires an interest in a not-for-profit entity to effectuate the
22 administration of the mission of the public trust, that entity shall
23 not be subject to the Oklahoma Open Meeting Act and the Oklahoma
24 Open Records Act. Any information submitted to or compiled by the
